Pick an alignment style and stick to it.  Either.
		pgmap = devm_kzalloc(dev,
			struct_size(pgmap, ranges, dev_dax->nr_range - 1),
			GFP_KERNEL);

or go long for readability and do
		pgmap = devm_kzalloc(dev,
				     struct_size(pgmap, ranges, dev_dax->nr_range - 1),
				     GFP_KERNEL);



